  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Today?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was devastated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, it was much smaller.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The previous ghetto was all the way to Leszno Street, the-- the second ghetto reduction.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But after 1942, when there was a total evacuation of Jews-- I mean deportation of Jews from Warsaw ghetto, the Germans minimized the size of the ghetto from Leszno to Gesia Street and then to Niska Street and from Okopowa to-- to the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Muranow and is the garden of Krasinski.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At the gate-- at the garden of Krasinski was a gate, entrance gate to this ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at that time, some of the Germans were trying to lure Antek Zuckerman into negotiation of surrendering to the Germans on the conditions recognized by the international law, by coming out with a white flag.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "However, they were met with shots from the Franciszkanska Street ghetto-- I mean factory of Antek Zuckerman, who refused to meet with any Germans participating in negotiation of evacuation of any people from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were told by the-- by the people who were coming from-- from the bunkers of the order bunkers and headquarters about this event.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we knew that-- that these were quite reliable people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Now in our weapons, we had small Molotov cocktail.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't know at the time that they were calling this Molotov cocktail.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they were loaded bottles with little sticking-out knot, and just to be ignited and thrown.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We used them during the period of time when the 360 people were being taken apart, when we noticed that there were approaching vehicles from the Gesia Street [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] gate.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And somehow we succeeded to stop them.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
